title: One Bedroom One Bathroom Available in August
posting_body: Thank you for your interest in Latitude 47 Apartment Homes.
These new apartment homes are located in the heart of University Place.
With the best of urban living in mind, this will be the place you will be proud to call home.
All of our apartments feature fully equipped Pewter GE appliances, full size washer and dryer, linen closet, pantry and spacious bedrooms and closets.
We offer Granite countertops on our 1st, 4th and 5th floors.
All apartments come with either a Juliet or full balcony with stunning views of either Mt. Rainer or the Olympic Mountains.
Some of our amenities include fitness center, hot tub, resident lounge, and rooftop court yard featuring BBQ area and cozy fireplace.
Each apartment comes with a reserved parking spot in the garage with extra parking for guests, electric car charging stations and bike storage available for your convenience.
